metadata.name: Official 2022 Freshmaker Industries Decentraland #MVMF Poster
metadata.description: We are proud to present the official Freshmaker Industries OG Smash Stage poster created for the 2022 Decentraland Metaverse Music Festival created by artist SkyIlls (Twitter @SkyIlls). It is an absolute honor to be chosen to curate this stage as it was designed to showcase artists that have spent time performing in Decentraland and the community that has helped with these events. All of the artists on the lineup have become friends of mine over the past year and I either met them at their DCL shows or have helped them throw their events. We appreciate the support in joining us 11/12 at the event and hope you have a good time! Feel free to tip the artists on show day and most importantly, get out there and burn up the dancefloor!
